title: 2018 NFL Draft Winners and Losers (Football 04/29)
description:
The 2018 NFL Draft is in the books, so Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech are firing up the podcast machine to discuss who won and who lost. The Cardinals landed their franchise quarterback but did they do enough to warrant a celebration? Should the Giants get a pass for going a running back early? Did the Packers put themselves in position to reclaim the NFC North? Are the Seahawks the worst team in the NFC West? Is Dak Prescott a dead man walking with his receiver corps? Did John Elway revamp the Broncos on the fly? Why didn't that stupid parrot say anything?? All those questions answered plus much much more.
